I come in and load the program
    Log in or create username (find user by username)
Find out what I can do (CLI will list options)
    1. View my Wishlist
    2. View my Read Books 
    3. View Shelf List 
        a. select a shelf
            i. view contents
            ii. modify shelf
            iii. modify contents
    4. Modify shelves
        a. create Shelf
        b. delete shelf 
            i. which shelf?
        c. rename shelf
            i. which shelf?
        d. modify contents
            i. which shelf?
    5. Search books 
        a. add to a shelf
        b. search again
    6. Search author (stretch)
    7. Exit
    
